From: quark <quark@triskelion>
Subject: configure: register steam_helper program in Wine build system

Adds WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE entry so Proton's steam_helper (steam.exe) builds
as a Wine builtin program. Source symlinked from Proton's steam_helper/ into
programs/steam_helper/. Requires autoconf regeneration after applying.

---
diff --git a/configure.ac b/configure.ac
index 33860c12462..dbaa9b6d2da 100644
--- a/configure.ac
+++ b/configure.ac
@@ -3595,6 +3595,7 @@ WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(programs/shutdown)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(programs/sort)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(programs/spoolsv)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(programs/start)
+WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(programs/steam_helper)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(programs/subst)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(programs/svchost)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(programs/systeminfo)
